name: M2e-antlr4
body:
### M2E Connector for Antlr4
This is a basic Antlr4 connector for M2E based on the Antlr3 connector originally available from Sonatype and now available [here] (https://github.com/tesla/m2eclipse-antlr).

### Eclipse update site can be found at (http://will-lauer.github.io/m2e-antlr4/site)

### Authors and Contributors
Plugin updated for antlr4 by @will-lauer
